description: Proficient in JavaScript, responsible for developing interactive and dynamic user interfaces. Collaborates with design and backend teams to ensure seamless integration of JavaScript functionalities.
Manage social media accounts and develop engaging content strategies. Stay updated with the latest trends and use different analytics to optimize social media presence.
Specializes in implementing visual elements that users see and interact with in a web application. Team up with back-end developers to ensure the overall design, experience and functionality.
Develop and execute content strategies to attract and retain customers. Utilize data-driven insights to create compelling and targeted content for various digital platforms and social sites.
